data.text:
Banned Individuals

The persons listed below have been advised by JCPD or JCHA Management that they are not to enter upon any JCHA owned or managed property at any time. The listing of any individual’s name on this list should not be interpreted as a statement or indication of any criminal wrong doing on the part of the individual. This information is provided to you to help you comply with your lease. Please be advised that only adults are listed below.

Contact Authorities

If you have any questions regarding this list or question if a certain juvenile is banned from the property, please contact the Community Policing Department at (423) 926-3339.
